In General:
	* Update the whole framework to be more general
	* Introduce the idea of sensors and actuators as components of an agent, towards simple real world robot simulation
	* Implement some more interesting objects for the world and effects on agents
	* Improve collision physics, and smoothness of animation

Implement in ga/crossover:
	* All crossover other than SinglePoint

Implement in ga/selection:
	* SUS
	* Random
	* Truncation
